Package: Lense
Type: Package
Title: Optimizing Data Preprocessing in Single-Cell Omics Using LLMs
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-07-16
Author: Jingyun Liu, Zhicheng Ji
Maintainer: Jingyun Liu <Jingyun.liu2@duke.edu>
Description: An R package that integrates OpenAI GPT-4 API for automated selection of optimal preprocessing pipelines in single-cell omics analysis, 
             using UMAP visualization comparison and iterative optimization. Lense systematically evaluates multiple preprocessing strategies 
             and selects the optimal pipeline without requiring manual parameter tuning.
Encoding: UTF-8
License: MIT
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports: Seurat,
         ggplot2,
         mclust,
         Matrix,
         httr,
         jsonlite,
         base64enc
Suggests: knitr,
          rmarkdown,
          markdown
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
NeedsCompilation: no
